    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2021 BMW M2 Competition in stunning Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle is the definition of showroom perfection, having covered only 4,200 miles under the care of a single meticulous owner. The exterior is flawless, protected from day one with a full-body XPEL Ultimate Plus paint protection film (PPF) and a professional ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains swirl-free and glass-like. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with contrast blue stitching remains in pristine condition; the bolsters show absolutely no wear, the carpets are spotless, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with every service performed ahead of schedule at authorized BMW centers. It has been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. Included with the sale are all original keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive folder of every service receipt. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
